# project title
Online_Retail_sales

## project Description
This project focuses on analyzing an online retail sales dataset to understand sales patterns, customers behaviour and business performance.The data was cleaned by handling missing values, remove duplicates, correcting data types and perform Exploratory data analysis(EDA).And visualizations to derive meaningful insights from the dataset.

## Objectives
* To analyze online retail sales data to understand business performance
* To perform data cleaning by handling missing values and duplicates
* To convert and correct data types for accurate analysis
* To identify top customers and high-performing countries
* To analyze sales trends based on time (hour, month, year)
* To visualize data using charts for better understanding
* To detect outliers in quantity and price

